TY  - JOUR
TI  - On the Invariance of the Lagrange Multiplier Test with Respect to Certain Changes in the Alternative Hypothesis
AU  - Godfrey, L. G.
AB  - [This paper examines some implications of the observation that the same Lagrange multiplier test is sometimes appropriate for quite different alternative hypotheses. A characterization of the class of such alternatives is developed which suggests a simple approach to testing for misspecification, and the consequences for finite sample power properties are examined by Monte Carlo experiments.]
