TY  - JOUR
TI  - Second Thoughts on Wald's Cost-of-Living Index and Frisch's Double Expenditure Method
AU  - Balk, Bert M.
AB  - [In this paper it is demonstrated that Wald's price index is the true cost-of-living index corresponding to a utility function of the form (x - γ)′ A (x - γ). Within this framework Frisch's double expenditure method and a related proposal of Samuelson are discussed.]
